							| Hybrid UX/UI Developer with a background in Software Engineering and 5+ years of experience bridging the gap between creative design and technical implementation. Specialist in building scalable design systems, component-driven UIs, and responsive interfaces for Web and React Native. Proven ability to convert complex UX concepts into production-ready frontend code, optimizing development handoffs and ensuring visual consistency across platforms.
					
					
